      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had little snakes, garter snakes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had also frogs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had frogs with-- they have long tail with-- what is that called?",
